        },
        {
            "title": "地產｜首岸第1期爆收7600票  超購33倍即推新價單",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"地產｜首岸第1期爆收7600票 超購33倍即推新價單\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">地產｜首岸第1期爆收7600票 超購33倍即推新價單</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由恒基地產（0012）、希慎興業（0014）及帝國集團聯手打造的紅磡庇利街「首岸」第1期人氣爆棚，實際票數在點算中，昨截票預估累收高達7600張認購表，以周六首推218伙計，超額認購33倍，創近期新盤熱度紀錄。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場反應遠超預期，發展商即展開次輪銷售部署，第三張價單即將推出並輕微加價，仍主推第1期第2座單位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">首岸位處紅磡海濱黃金地段，預計2027年8月入伙，分四期提供1296伙，標準戶型由2房339呎至3房642呎。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">展銷廳昨日仍有大批準買家排隊，S/A組大戶預計搶購逾133伙，恒生銀行提供2.73%定息按揭優惠。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2-%E9%A6%96%E5%B2%B8%E7%AC%AC1%E6%9C%9F%E7%88%86%E6%94%B67600%E7%A5%A8-%E8%B6%85%E8%B3%BC33%E5%80%8D%E5%8D%B3%E6%8E%A8%E6%96%B0%E5%83%B9%E5%96%AE-103619508.html",
